flowchart TB
    Internet((Internet)) --> IGW[Internet Gateway]
    IGW --> Public[Public Subnets]
    Public --> ALB[Application Load Balancer SG: HTTPS 443]
    Public --> NAT[NAT Gateway]
    ALB --> App[Private App Subnets SG: App Port 8080]
    App --> DB[Isolated Data Subnets SG: DB Port 5432]
    App --> NAT
    NAT --> IGW
    DB -. No default internet route .- X[Blocked Internet Egress]
    App --> VPCE[VPC Endpoints]
    DB --> VPCE
    VPCFlow[VPC Flow Logs] --> CW[CloudWatch Logs]
    VPCFlow --> S3[S3 Archive]
